Hello i'm Poopsi! a discord bot developer, and I have decided to help new discord bot creators like yourself on how to make a discord bot in discord.js.

Here I have everything written down step by step on how to set your discord bot up.

___________________________________________________________________________________

                        Things you are required to install
___________________________________________________________________________________


In your terminal:
    -type "npm install nodejs"
    -type "npm install discord.js"

___________________________________________________________________________________

                        Links that will help you make the bot
___________________________________________________________________________________


1. https://discord.com/developers/applications

2. https://discord.js.org/#/

3. www.youtube.com

___________________________________________________________________________________

                        Basic setup of the bot
___________________________________________________________________________________

1. Aquire your discord bot token at the your discord developer portal.

2. go to ./Utils/botCofig.json and replace "example-token" with your bot token.

3. Make sure you have installed discord.js (see line 13)

4. Make sure your bot is in your discord server.

5. type "node index.js" in your terminal, and watch the magic happen.


